e, into its fantastical realms of magic and wonder.An English-only edition.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aArabsvFolklore. 0aFairy tales. 0aFolklorezArab countries. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / Middle Eastern.2bisacsh1 aFudge, Bruce, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIrwin, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.18574/nyu/9781479894963.001.000140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781479894963423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781479894963/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles